	<Title>
		Laryngospasm: What causes it?
	</Title>
	<Abstract>
		Laryngospasm is a brief spasm of the vocal cords, which temporarily interrupts breathing.
	</Abstract>
	<Question>
		What causes laryngospasm?
	</Question>
